2
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The knight selection exam is the 
empire's largest annual event.</i></font>

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:19,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Go get 'em!</font>

4
00:00:19,300 --> 00:00:21,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Come on, man! I've bet it all on you!</font>

5
00:00:24,160 --> 00:00:30,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The official name of the nation everyone 
calls "the empire" is the Meeres Empire.</i></font>

6
00:00:30,440 --> 00:00:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Meeres" is an ancient  word 
meaning "warrior."</i></font>

7
00:00:33,580 --> 00:00:37,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Indeed, in the Meeres Empire, 
a nation of warriors,</i></font>

8
00:00:37,850 --> 00:00:42,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>military might is the one and only 
path to merit-based success,</i></font>

9
00:00:42,800 --> 00:00:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and that success is decided 
by the knight selection exam.</i></font>

10
00:00:48,340 --> 00:00:52,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The exam draws the attention 
of many in the empire,</i></font>

11
00:00:52,220 --> 00:00:54,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but this year, in particular,</i></font>

12
00:00:54,180 --> 00:00:59,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>sees a prince personally serving as 
the head judge, a first in history.</i></font>

13
00:01:00,420 --> 00:01:06,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>People have gathered at the venue 
in droves for a chance to see him.</i></font>

14
00:01:23,890 --> 00:01:24,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough!</font>

15
00:01:26,530 --> 00:01:28,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just no use!</font>

16
00:01:28,360 --> 00:01:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow... No one can even 
lay a finger on him.</font>

17
00:01:32,130 --> 00:01:34,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's the Wise Prince...</font>

18
00:01:41,910 --> 00:01:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This year's exam is 
considered far</font>

19
00:01:44,910 --> 00:01:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">more exciting than those of past years.</font>

20
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's important is the outcome.</font>

21
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:54,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The knight selection exam is 
for choosing worthy soldiers.</font>

22
00:01:54,710 --> 00:01:58,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I look forward to seeing</font>

23
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:00,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what sort of fighter Noah chooses.</font>

24
00:02:01,780 --> 00:02:04,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Examinee Number 152, come forward!</font>

25
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:33,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The sun will be setting soon.</i></font>

26
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:36,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No particularly noteworthy 
candidates today, I suppose.</i></font>

27
00:02:39,250 --> 00:02:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The next test will be 
the last of the day!</font>

28
00:03:02,650 --> 00:03:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This... won't... stop me!</font>

29
00:03:19,270 --> 00:03:20,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm so sor—</font>

30
00:03:20,670 --> 00:03:21,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop right there!</font>

31
00:03:23,260 --> 00:03:24,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master!</font>

32
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:31,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boy, she's really done it.</font>

33
00:03:31,470 --> 00:03:33,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She actually wounded the prince!</font>

34
00:03:33,650 --> 00:03:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The law's gonna come down hard on her.</font>

35
00:03:36,410 --> 00:03:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let her go.</font>

36
00:03:37,340 --> 00:03:40,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But, Your Highness, this woman just...</font>

37
00:03:40,270 --> 00:03:41,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said, let her go.</font>

38
00:03:41,810 --> 00:03:43,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Of course.</font>

39
00:03:45,410 --> 00:03:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your name?</font>

40
00:03:46,870 --> 00:03:50,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-My name is Shirley Grantz.</font>

41
00:03:50,350 --> 00:03:51,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You pass.</font>

42
00:03:56,750 --> 00:04:01,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't name my standards,
but she's clearly an instant pass.</font>

43
00:04:01,250 --> 00:04:02,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She passed?</font>

44
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:04,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's forgiving the woman who wounded him?</font>

45
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:06,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How generous His Highness is!</font>

46
00:04:23,570 --> 00:04:25,530
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#817c4f"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="10">Born Blessed, So I'll Obtain Ultimate Power</font></b></font></font></font>

