00:05:40,380 --> 00:05:43,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's some fine armor.
Do you own it?</font>

49
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes. It's been handed down 
in my family for generations.</font>

50
00:05:47,570 --> 00:05:48,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, um...</font>

51
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:52,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what did you mean when you 
said... that I passed?</font>

52
00:05:52,580 --> 00:05:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is my sentence?</font>

53
00:05:54,430 --> 00:05:57,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For wounding me "by mistake," you mean?</font>

54
00:05:57,650 --> 00:05:58,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

55
00:05:58,820 --> 00:06:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is no such thing.</font>

56
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:03,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you to attack me, after all.</font>

57
00:06:06,670 --> 00:06:10,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stand. Use that thrust on me again.</font>

58
00:06:10,310 --> 00:06:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

59
00:06:11,660 --> 00:06:13,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you are a knight, 
then follow my orders.</font>

60
00:06:15,090 --> 00:06:16,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'll excuse me.</font>

61
00:06:26,140 --> 00:06:26,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come.</font>

62
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:33,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One... more...</font>

63
00:06:33,990 --> 00:06:38,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this? It won't budge!</font>

64
00:06:38,810 --> 00:06:42,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is what I could have done if I'd 
really wanted to block your attack.</font>

65
00:06:42,430 --> 00:06:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did not wound me "by mistake."</font>

66
00:06:46,670 --> 00:06:49,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A knight's job is to follow orders.</font>

67
00:06:49,740 --> 00:06:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to see if you would 
execute my orders faithfully.</font>

68
00:06:53,170 --> 00:06:57,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't need a knight who's going 
to hold back for fear of me.</font>

69
00:06:57,800 --> 00:07:01,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You came at me in earnest twice, 
even after wounding me.</font>

70
00:07:01,980 --> 00:07:03,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have what it takes.</font>

71
00:07:03,820 --> 00:07:06,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your resolve was that strong?</font>

72
00:07:09,380 --> 00:07:14,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, Shirley Grantz, swear my undying 
loyalty to you for the rest of my life.</font>

73
00:07:14,830 --> 00:07:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good.</font>

74
00:07:16,190 --> 00:07:18,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That exaggerated gesture 
I've seen in plays...</i></font>

75
00:07:18,910 --> 00:07:22,070
